name: StaticBucketMap_containsKeyTest
description: Unit tests for the containsKey method of the StaticBucketMap class.

test_cases.name: testContainsKey_KeyExists
test_cases.description: Tests the containsKey method when the key exists in the map.

test_cases.name: testContainsKey_KeyDoesNotExist
test_cases.description: Tests the containsKey method when the key does not exist in the map.

test_cases.name: testContainsKey_NullKeyExists
test_cases.description: Tests the containsKey method when the null key exists in the map.

test_cases.name: testContainsKey_NullKeyDoesNotExist
test_cases.description: Tests the containsKey method when the null key does not exist in the map.

test_cases.name: testContainsKey_AfterRemove
test_cases.description: Tests the containsKey method after removing a key from the map.

test_cases.name: testContainsKey_AfterClear
test_cases.description: Tests the containsKey method after clearing the map.

test_cases.name: testContainsKey_AfterPutAll
test_cases.description: Tests the containsKey method after adding all entries from another map.

test_cases.name: testContainsKey_AfterPut
test_cases.description: Tests the containsKey method after adding a key-value pair to the map.
